: [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chantelle_Houghton\", \"score\": 0.9999999999961346, \"rank\": 2.04244393750544e-12, \"text\": \"Chantelle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chantelle_Houghton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chantelle_Houghton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing gloves\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"six years\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"one last shotto\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A former stand-out junior who won two European gold medals and one world bronze, Reid had been forced to stop boxing at the age of 18 after a crippling diagnosis of degenerative disc disease.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two European gold medals\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"one world bronze\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"a crippling diagnosis\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"degenerative disc disease\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Six years of careful recuperation sparked a spectacular return which not only saw her sweep through the English National Championships but go beyond tograb an improbable qualifying placefor the ParisOlympicsat the first available opportunity.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Six years\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"careful recuperation\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular return\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the English National Championships\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"tograb\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympicsat\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's crazy to think I managed to come back and qualify for the Paris Olympics within a year, but I made it happen,\\\" Reid told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came back gradually and targeted the nationals and from there it all went so fast, I got letter after letter first from England and then GB, and then I got the chance to go to the first qualifier and I did it with six weeks of preparation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1318, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9704862551541386, \"rank\": 0.030151251606498175, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9600211309037388, \"rank\": 0.04076491308017685, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nationals\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"letter\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"letter\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"six weeks\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old from Derby had made boxing her life from an early age, rising swiftly through the junior ranks and inflicting a notable defeat on Turkey's Busenaz Surmeneli, who would go on to claim 66kg gold in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derby_County_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.8339278045403015, \"rank\": 0.19139055314623987, \"text\": \"Derby\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derby_County_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derby_County_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1586, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7435539723361663, \"rank\": 0.3412059131234257, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999127164014845, \"rank\": 8.713044686261945e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the junior ranks\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"a notable defeat\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"66kg gold\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But having gone through the majority of her youth career in near constant pain, Reid was strongly advised to take an extended break or face consequences potentially much more serious than the end of her boxing career in later life.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"her youth career\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"constant pain\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"an extended break\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"consequences\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"her boxing career\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"later life\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was in so much pain I was struggling to sleep at night, and I went to see a couple of specialists who told me if I did not stop it could have consequences further down the line,\\\" added Reid.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much pain\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"specialists\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"consequences\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"Reid\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not want to end up in a wheelchair by the age of 30, but I knew it could get worse, so I made the decision to stop and at that point I did not think I would be able to box again.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wheelchair\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy 185+ fights a year on DAZN, the Global Home of Boxing Never miss a fight from top promoters.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \